---
import ProductLayout from '../../../layouts/ProductLayout.astro';
---

<ProductLayout title="ST1200 Industrial Static Eliminator Fan | Wide-Area ESD Control | DGSDK"
  description="ST-1200 industrial static eliminator fan for wide-area ESD control. Suitable for large workstations, industrial packaging lines, and display manufacturing."
  image="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-1200.jpg">
  <section class="product-detail-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <a href="/products">Products</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <a href="/products/static-eliminator">Static Eliminator</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span>ST1200</span>
      </div>

      <div class="product-top">
        <div class="product-gallery">
          <div class="product-main-image slider-wrapper">
            <button class="slider-arrow left" id="prevImage">‹</button>
            <img
              id="mainProductImage"
              src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-1200.jpg"
              alt="ST1200 Horizontal Ion Fan"
            />
            <button class="slider-arrow right" id="nextImage">›</button>
          </div>

          <div class="product-thumbs">
            <img
              class="thumb-image active-thumb"
              src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-1200.jpg"
              alt="ST1200 Thumbnail"
              data-full="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-1200.jpg"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="product-summary">
          <h1>ST1200 Horizontal Ion Fan</h1>
          <p class="product-short-desc">
            Horizontal desktop ion fan with wide airflow coverage, suitable for larger
            anti-static zones and workstation-side installation.
          </p>

          <div class="product-actions">
            <button class="quote-btn" type="button">Get a Quote</button>
            <a href="https://wa.me/61436605126" target="_blank" class="whatsapp-btn">WhatsApp</a>
          </div>

          <div class="product-highlights">
            <div class="highlight-item">
              <h4>Large Coverage</h4>
              <p>Air coverage reaches wide working areas for broader anti-static protection.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-item">
              <h4>Adjustable Airflow</h4>
              <p>Air volume can be adjusted according to process requirements.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-item">
              <h4>Built-in Generator</h4>
              <p>Integrated high-voltage generator supports stable ion output.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="detail-block">
        <h2>Product Description</h2>
        <p>
          The ST1200 horizontal ion fan provides a wide ionized air coverage area and is
          suitable for hanging horizontally or placing near workstations. It is developed
          for larger anti-static work zones requiring stable airflow and static control.
        </p>
        <p>
          It is commonly used in electronics manufacturing, workstation protection,
          packaging lines, and other industrial applications where wider electrostatic
          elimination coverage is needed.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="detail-block">
        <h2>Product Features</h2>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Wide-area horizontal anti-static airflow</li>
          <li>Adjustable air volume for different working needs</li>
          <li>Suitable for hanging or workstation-side installation</li>
          <li>Built-in high-voltage generator for stable performance</li>
          <li>Designed for broader industrial electrostatic protection</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="detail-block">
        <h2>Technical Advantages</h2>
        <div class="advantage-grid">
          <div class="advantage-card blue">
            <h3>Wide Reach</h3>
            <p>Extended air coverage helps protect larger working surfaces and lines.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="advantage-card yellow">
            <h3>Adjustable</h3>
            <p>Airflow can be tuned according to product size and process speed.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="advantage-card green">
            <h3>Integrated</h3>
            <p>Built-in ion generation system simplifies installation and operation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="detail-block">
        <h2>Technical Specifications</h2>
        <div class="spec-table-wrap">
          <table class="spec-table">
            <tr><td>Operating Voltage</td><td>110V / 60Hz or 220V / 50Hz</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Power</td><td>40W to 80W</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Operating Temperature</td><td>-10℃ to 50℃</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Dimensions</td><td>1280mm(L) × 215mm(W) × 190mm(H)</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Weight</td><td>14.5Kg</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Air Coverage</td><td>140cm × 120cm</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Air Volume</td><td>150–360CFM</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Ion Balance</td><td>0V ±10V</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="detail-block">
        <h2>Industry Applications</h2>
        <div class="application-tags">
          <span>Electronics</span>
          <span>Workstations</span>
          <span>Packaging</span>
          <span>Inspection Lines</span>
          <span>Assembly Operations</span>
          <span>Wide-Area Static Control</span>
        </div>
      </section>


      <section class="detail-block">
        <h2>Application Scenarios</h2>
        <div class="scenario-list">
          <div class="scenario-item">
            <h3>Large-Format Production Lines</h3>
            <p>The ST1200's 1280 mm body and 140 cm × 120 cm coverage area make it the right choice for protecting entire conveyor widths or full-length assembly stations in one unit. Electronics manufacturers use it to provide a continuous ion field above PCB conveyor lines and panel staging areas, eliminating the need to position multiple smaller blowers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="scenario-item">
            <h3>Optical Film and Display Panel Manufacturing</h3>
            <p>Static charge during film lamination, cutting, and inspection causes dust adhesion and optical defects that reduce yield. The ST1200's wide even airflow covers the full panel width, neutralizing charge before dust can settle on glass substrates or optical films.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="scenario-item">
            <h3>Industrial Packaging Stations</h3>
            <p>Packaging operations involving polypropylene bags, shrink film, and anti-static packaging materials often generate significant charge. A single ST1200 unit positioned above the packaging station provides full-width coverage, preventing film cling and protecting sensitive packaged components from ESD during the final stage of production.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="detail-block">
        <h2>How to Choose the Right Ionizing Blower</h2>
        <p>The ST1200 is the right choice when you need coverage exceeding 1 meter in width with a single unit. For individual workstations or smaller benches, the <a href="/products/static-eliminator/st-101a">ST101A</a> or <a href="/products/static-eliminator/st-104a">ST104A</a> provide more compact and cost-effective solutions. For inline applications where the ion source must be integrated into a conveyor frame rather than positioned above it, an <a href="/products/static-eliminator/st-e-series">ion bar</a> or <a href="/products/static-eliminator/st-g-series">ST-G Series intelligent ion rod</a> is typically more appropriate.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="detail-block faq-block">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3 class="faq-question">What is the ST1200 designed for?</h3>
            <p class="faq-answer">The ST1200 is a large-format horizontal ion fan providing 140 cm × 120 cm coverage across a 1280 mm body. It is designed to neutralize static electricity across full-width production line workstations, display panel staging areas, and industrial packaging stations in a single unit.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3 class="faq-question">How does the ST1200 compare to the ST104A?</h3>
            <p class="faq-answer">The ST1200 provides approximately 2.3× the coverage area of the ST104A and is suited for full production line width protection. The ST104A is better for individual mid-sized workstations where the larger ST1200 footprint would be impractical.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3 class="faq-question">Does the ST1200 require compressed air?</h3>
            <p class="faq-answer">No. The ST1200 uses integrated fan motors and requires only a standard power outlet — 110V/60Hz or 220V/50Hz — with power consumption of 40W to 80W depending on the airflow setting.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3 class="faq-question">Can the ST1200 be mounted overhead?</h3>
            <p class="faq-answer">Yes. The ST1200 can be ceiling-mounted or suspended above a production line to deliver downward ionized airflow across a wide area. Contact us for mounting bracket options.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3 class="faq-question">What ion balance does the ST1200 maintain?</h3>
            <p class="faq-answer">The ST1200 maintains an ion balance of 0V ±10V across its full coverage area, meeting the standard requirements for ESD-sensitive electronics manufacturing environments.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3 class="faq-question">Is the ST1200 suitable for film and optical industries?</h3>
            <p class="faq-answer">Yes. The ST1200's wide horizontal coverage makes it well suited for optical film lamination, display panel assembly, and coating processes where electrostatic charge causes dust adhesion and surface defects.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="detail-block">
        <div class="related-slider-wrap" data-current="st-1200">
          <div class="related-slider-header">
            <h2>Related Products</h2>
            <div class="related-slider-nav">
              <button class="related-slider-btn related-slider-prev" type="button">‹</button>
              <button class="related-slider-btn related-slider-next" type="button">›</button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="related-slider-track">
            <a href="/products/static-eliminator/st-g-series" class="related-slide-card" data-key="st-g-series">
              <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-g.jpg" alt="ST-G Series" loading="lazy" />
              <h4>ST-G Series Intelligent Ion Rod</h4>
            </a>
            <a href="/products/static-eliminator/st-e-series" class="related-slide-card" data-key="st-e-series">
              <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-e.jpg" alt="ST-E Series" loading="lazy" />
              <h4>ST-E Series Intelligent Ion Rod</h4>
            </a>
            <a href="/products/static-eliminator/st-f-series" class="related-slide-card" data-key="st-f-series">
              <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-f.jpg" alt="ST-F Series" loading="lazy" />
              <h4>ST-F Series Intelligent Ion Rod</h4>
            </a>
            <a href="/products/static-eliminator/st-s200" class="related-slide-card" data-key="st-s200">
              <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-s200.jpg" alt="ST-S200" loading="lazy" />
              <h4>ST-S200 Mini Ionizer Fan</h4>
            </a>
            <a href="/products/static-eliminator/st-101a" class="related-slide-card" data-key="st-101a">
              <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-101a.jpg" alt="ST101A" loading="lazy" />
              <h4>ST101A Table Ionizing Air Blower</h4>
            </a>
            <a href="/products/static-eliminator/st-104a" class="related-slide-card" data-key="st-104a">
              <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-104a.jpg" alt="ST104A" loading="lazy" />
              <h4>ST104A Horizontal Ion Blower</h4>
            </a>
            <a href="/products/static-eliminator/st-1200" class="related-slide-card" data-key="st-1200">
              <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-1200.jpg" alt="ST1200" loading="lazy" />
              <h4>ST1200 Horizontal Ion Fan</h4>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>

